==Chinese==
===[[Mandarin]]===
[[Pinyin]]: yíhàn
===[[Min Nan]]===
[[POJ]]: ûi-hām
===Noun===
# [[regret]]
#: ''[[这]][[是]][[他]][[终身]][[的]]'''遗憾'''''
#: ''This is a life-long '''regret''' of his''

===Adjective===
# [[regrettable]]
#: ''[[父亲]]'''遗憾'''[[的]][[是]][[生前]][[没]][[能]][[写]][[完]][[那]][[本]][[书]]''
#: ''It is '''regrettable''' that my father was unable to finish writing that book before his death''
# [[regrettable]] (as used in diplomatic circles)
#: ''[[非常]]'''遗憾'''，[[贵]][[国]][[政府]][[不予]][[合作]]''
#: ''It is very '''regrettable''' that your country's government declines to cooperate''
# [[sorry]]
#: ''[[非常]]'''遗憾'''，[[我]][[无法]][[帮助]][[你]]''
#: ''I'm so '''sorry''', there is no way for me to help you''
# too bad
#: ''[[你]][[不能]][[来]]，[[真]][[是]][[太]]'''遗憾'''[[了]]''
#: ''It is really '''too bad''' that you cannot come''

===Verb===
# to regret
#: ''[[令]][[人]]'''遗憾'''''
#: ''cause one '''to regret'''''

